      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Mandra's letter$<BR>Thank you for helping me with finding my little sister. I heard it from Roy.<BR>Well, I also thought it was strange….<BR>Roy can't possibly get out of <FONT color=#2b2723>Saint Haven, </FONT> so I wondered how he would manage to go outside so many times.</html>]]></talk_question>
